data.description: Beautiful 4/4/3 w/Office+ bonus room+ 45x30 dream shop is located in the prestigious Westwood neighborhood. Totally updated which includes a brand new roof w/new carpet in the Main bedroom, new paint in all bedrooms/bathrooms office/both living/dining rooms, & kitchen/cabinets. The character-filled interior includes 2 separate good-sized living areas both equipped with a relaxing fireplace and a flow-through kitchen living/dining area. Natural lighting creates a perfect ambiance throughout. Main bedroom overlooks the pool and backyard. Main bathroom has a walk-in benched shower w/separate, soaker tub/double vanities. The built for entertaining covered patio w/electric pool cover creates the perfect ambience for making wonderful memories.  All will enjoy a prime location in a most desirable part of Lubbock and discover why the neighborhood is much beloved by its community. Appreciate the benefits of a spacious 3-car attached garage sitting on .87 acres and a huge wood workers dream shop
